            "author_title": "Environmentalist, Founder of Dirt"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_RxABEK": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "quote_short": "<p>Beautifully complex and vibrant, Cala Falcó at spring delivers elegant botanical depth as a sophisticated non-alcoholic aperitivo.</p>",
            "cta_label": "Read full testimonial",
            "cta_link": "",
            "open_in_new_tab": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Cala_Falc_at_Spring_non-alcoholic_aperitivo_drink.jpg",
            "author": "Claire Warner",
            "author_title": "Global Non-Alcoholic Drinks Industry Thought Leader"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_xG3TVA": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "quote_short": "<p>Cala Falcó at spring is light, crisp and wonderfully thirst-quenching, with beautiful notes of rosemary and a subtle sea-water minerality that captures the essence of the Mediterranean. The perfect alcohol free drink.</p>",
            "cta_label": "Read full testimonial",
            "cta_link": "",
            "open_in_new_tab": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Cala_Falc_at_Spring_bottle_surrounded_by_rosemary.png",
            "author": "Emily Horner",
            "author_title": "Non-Alcoholic Drinks Influencer"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Cnhen3": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "quote_short": "<p>Cala Falcó at Spring is fresh, layered, and complex. An interesting balance of floral lift, with deeper savoury notes that make you want another glass!</p>",
            "cta_label": "",
            "cta_link": "",
            "open_in_new_tab": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Cala_Falc_at_Spring_bottle.png",
            "author": "Dr. Josh Allison",
            "author_title": "Explorer, Adventurer and Doctor"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_VEVtTE": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "quote_short": "<p>It’s tastes like summer in a glass, refreshing as well as having a complex taste. It feels like a luxurious treat.</p>",
            "cta_label": "",
            "cta_link": "",
            "open_in_new_tab": true,
