    "content_cards_FExKVR": {
      "type": "content-cards",
      "blocks": {
        "card_QXgTBJ": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "",
            "show_icon": true,
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Vector_28.png",
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Cala Falcó produces limited batches using hand picked wild botanicals  growing during the relevant season. The botanicals go through an  artisanal process unique to Cala Falco. </p>"
          }
        },
        "card_KEfJVJ": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "",
            "show_icon": true,
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Vector_29.png",
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Steam-distilled hydrosols of farm-grown rosemary and mastic—fortified with their own  essential-oil fractions, form the botanical backbone, joined by  cold-pressed organic Mallorcan lemon juice. </p>"
          }
        },
        "card_YcL4KR": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "",
            "show_icon": true,
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Vector_30.png",
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Mineral-rich, deep-sea storm water is filtered and “re-structured,” then blended with Cala Falcó estate honey and a touch of stevia to balance the  invigorating herbal profile. </p>"
          }
        },
        "card_YgDrM3": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "",
            "show_icon": true,
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Vector_31.png",
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>A vibrant pink hue from mastic berries crowns the blend, which is gently  pasteurized for stability, capturing the spirit of a springtime walk  along Cala Falcó in every restorative sip. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "card_QXgTBJ",
        "card_KEfJVJ",
        "card_YcL4KR",
        "card_YgDrM3"
      ],
      "name": "Content cards",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "HARNESSING NATURE",
        "description": "<p>Here are just some of the steps we take to harness the botanicals you will find in each and every sip.</p>",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding-block-start": 0,
        "padding-block-end": 80
      }
